tion for stronger bones and teeth.</p>\n<p>Imported and trusted by parents worldwide, Similac Gold 3 (800 g) is now available in Bangladesh through Probashi Bazar, ensuring 100% genuine quality and safe doorstep delivery for your little one&rsquo;s daily nutrition.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Key Benefits</p>\n<p>Suitable for toddlers aged 1&ndash;3 years</p>\n<p>Enriched with DHA, Lutein &amp; Vitamin E for brain and eye development</p>\n<p>Palm-oil-free for better digestion and nutrient absorption</p>\n<p>Supports stronger bones, teeth, and immunity</p>\n<p>Clinically tested and trusted by parents worldwide</p>\n<p>100% authentic imported product from Abbott</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Product Details</p>\n<p>Brand: Similac (Abbott)</p>\n<p>Origin: Imported (UAE / UK / Singapore variants)</p>\n<p>Net Weight: 800 g</p>\n<p>Age Group: 1&ndash;3 years</p>\n<p>Storage: Keep tightly closed in a cool, dry place. Use within 3 weeks after opening.</p>\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:153:\"Imported toddler formula for 1–3 years. DHA, Lutein & Vitamin E enriched to support brain, eye, and body development. Palm-oil-free and easy to digest.\";}s:11:\"\0*\0original\";a:6:{s:2:\"id\";i:101;s:10:\"product_id\";i:101;s:6:\"locale\";s:2:\"en\";s:4:\"name\";s:75:\"Similac Gold 3 (800 g) – Toddler Formula for 1–3 Years | Probashi Bazar\";s:11:\"description\";s:1420:\"<p>Similac Gold 3 is a premium growing-up formula specially made for toddlers aged 1&ndash;3 years. It provides complete and balanced nutrition to support rapid physical growth, brain development, and strong immunity during the early learning years.</p>\n<p>Formulated with DHA, Lutein, and Vitamin E, Similac Gold 3 helps improve brain and eye development, supporting better learning, focus, and memory. The formula is palm-oil-free, ensuring gentle digestion and improved calcium absorption for stronger bones and teeth.</p>\n<p>Imported and trusted by parents worldwide, Similac Gold 3 (800 g) is now available in Bangladesh through Probashi Bazar, ensuring 100% genuine quality and safe doorstep delivery for your little one&rsquo;s daily nutrition.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Key Benefits</p>\n<p>Suitable for toddlers aged 1&ndash;3 years</p>\n<p>Enriched with DHA, Lutein &amp; Vitamin E for brain and eye development</p>\n<p>Palm-oil-free for better digestion and nutrient absorption</p>\n<p>Supports stronger bones, teeth, and immunity</p>\n<p>Clinically tested and trusted by parents worldwide</p>\n<p>100% authentic imported product from Abbott</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Product Details</p>\n<p>Brand: Similac (Abbott)</p>\n<p>Origin: Imported (UAE / UK / Singapore variants)</p>\n<p>Net Weight: 800 g</p>\n<p>Age Group: 1&ndash;3 years</p>\n<p>Storage: Keep tightly closed in a cool, dry place. Use within 3 weeks after opening.</p>\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:153:\"Imported toddler formula for 1–3 years. DHA, Lutein & Vitamin E enriched to support brain, eye, and body development. Palm-oil-free and easy to digest.\";}s:10:\"\0*\0changes\";a:0:{}s:8:\"\0*\0casts\";a:0:{}s:17:\"\0*\0classCastCache\";a:0:{}s:21:\"\0*\0attributeCastCache\";a:0:{}s:13:\"\0*\0dateFormat\";N;s:10:\"\0*\0appends\";a:0:{}s:19:\"\0*\0dispatchesEvents\";a:0:{}s:14:\"\0*\0observables\";a:0:{}s:12:\"\0*\0relations\";a:0:{}s:10:\"\0*\0touches\";a:0:{}s:10:\"timestamps\";b:0;s:13:\"usesUniqueIds\";b:0;s:9:\"\0*\0hidden\";a:0:{}s:10:\"\0*\0visible\";a:0:{}s:11:\"\0*\0fillable\";a:3:{i:0;s:4:\"name\";i:1;s:11:\"description\";i:2;s:17:\"short_description\";}s:10:\"\0*\0guarded\";a:1:{i:0;s:1:\"*\";}}}s:28:\"\0*\0escapeWhenCastingToString\";b:0;}s:5:\"files\";O:39:\"Illuminate\\Database\\Eloquent\\Collection\":2:{s:8:\"\0*\0items\";a:1:{i:0;O:27:\"Modules\\Media\\Entities\\File\":30:{s:13:\"\0*\0connection\";s:5:\"mysql\";s:8:\"\0*\0table\";s:5:\"files\";s:13:\"\0*\0primaryKey\";s:2:\"id\";s:10:\"\0*\0keyType\";s:3:\"int\";s:12:\"incrementing\";b:1;s:7:\"\0*\0with\";a:0:{}s:12:\"\0*\0withCount\";a:0:{}s:19:\"preventsLazyLoading\";b:0;s:10:\