months, offering complete nutrition to support healthy growth, immunity, and brain development. Enriched with DHA, probiotics, and essential nutrients, this formula helps strengthen the immune system, support optimal cognitive development, and promote digestive health.</p>\n<p>The DHA (Omega-3 fatty acids) in Nan Optipro 2 plays a key role in brain development, while calcium and iron support the development of strong bones and healthy blood. With probiotics to aid in digestion and improve nutrient absorption, Nan Optipro 2 offers a balanced, easy-to-digest solution for your baby\'s nutritional needs.</p>\n<p>As a trusted Nestl&eacute; product, Nan Optipro 2 provides parents with confidence, ensuring that babies receive the highest quality nutrition for a strong, healthy start in life. Perfect for complementing breast milk and supporting babies through the critical first year of growth and development.</p>\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:178:\"Nan Optipro 2 800g: Advanced infant formula with probiotics, DHA, and essential nutrients to support healthy growth, immunity, and brain development for babies aged 6–12 months\";}s:11:\"\0*\0original\";a:6:{s:2:\"id\";i:96;s:10:\"product_id\";i:96;s:6:\"locale\";s:2:\"en\";s:4:\"name\";s:18:\"Nan Optipro 2 800g\";s:11:\"description\";s:1017:\"<p>Nan Optipro 2 800g is a scientifically advanced infant formula designed for babies aged 6&ndash;12 months, offering complete nutrition to support healthy growth, immunity, and brain development. Enriched with DHA, probiotics, and essential nutrients, this formula helps strengthen the immune system, support optimal cognitive development, and promote digestive health.</p>\n<p>The DHA (Omega-3 fatty acids) in Nan Optipro 2 plays a key role in brain development, while calcium and iron support the development of strong bones and healthy blood. With probiotics to aid in digestion and improve nutrient absorption, Nan Optipro 2 offers a balanced, easy-to-digest solution for your baby\'s nutritional needs.</p>\n<p>As a trusted Nestl&eacute; product, Nan Optipro 2 provides parents with confidence, ensuring that babies receive the highest quality nutrition for a strong, healthy start in life. Perfect for complementing breast milk and supporting babies through the critical first year of growth and development.</p>\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:178:\"Nan Optipro 2 800g: Advanced infant formula with probiotics, DHA, and essential nutrients to support healthy growth, immunity, and brain development for babies aged 6–12 months\";}s:10:\"\0*\0changes\";a:0:{}s:8:\"\0*\0casts\";a:0:{}s:17:\"\0*\0classCastCache\";a:0:{}s:21:\"\0*\0attributeCastCache\";a:0:{}s:13:\"\0*\0dateFormat\";N;s:10:\"\0*\0appends\";a:0:{}s:19:\"\0*\0dispatchesEvents\";a:0:{}s:14:\"\0*\0observables\";a:0:{}s:12:\"\0*\0relations\";a:0:{}s:10:\"\0*\0touches\";a:0:{}s:10:\"timestamps\";b:0;s:13:\"usesUniqueIds\";b:0;s:9:\"\0*\0hidden\";a:0:{}s:10:\"\0*\0visible\";a:0:{}s:11:\"\0*\0fillable\";a:3:{i:0;s:4:\"name\";i:1;s:11:\"description\";i:2;s:17:\"short_description\";}s:10:\"\0*\0guarded\";a:1:{i:0;s:1:\"*\";}}}s:28:\"\0*\0escapeWhenCastingToString\";b:0;}s:5:\"files\";O:39:\"Illuminate\\Database\\Eloquent\\Collection\":2:{s:8:\"\0*\0items\";a:1:{i:0;O:27:\"Modules\\Media\\Entities\\File\":30:{s:13:\"\0*\0connection\";s:5:\"mysql\";s:8:\"\0*\0table\";s:5:\"files\";s:13:\"\0*\0primaryKey\";s:2:\"id\";s:10:\"\0*\0keyType\";s:3:\"int\";s:12:\"incrementing\";b:1;s:7:\"\0*\0with\";a:0:{}s:12:\"\0*\0withCount\";a:0:{}s:19:\"preventsLazyLoading\";b:0;s:10:\"\0*\0perPage\";i:15;s:6:\"exists\";b:1;s:18:\"wasRecentlyCreated\";b:0;s:28:\"\0*\0escapeWhenCastingToString\";b:0;s:13:\"\0*\0attributes\";a:10:{s:2:\"id\";i:244;s:7:\"user_id\";i:1;s:8:\"filename\";s:8:\"nan2.png\";s:4:\"disk\";s:14:\"public_storage\";s:4:\"path\";s:50:\"media/RFIBKNWGdg3OKIZ4akiQPvMrbO96bjoNdz59HZZP.png\";s:9:\"extension\";s:3:\"png\";s:4:\"mime\";s:9:\"image/png\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"241289\";s:10:\"created_at\";s:19:\"2025-08-2