cked with DHA, calcium, and iron, Nan Optipro 3 promotes the development of strong bones, cognitive function, and overall well-being. As a trusted Nestl&eacute; product, it complements a balanced diet to ensure toddlers receive the nourishment they need for optimal growth and development.</p>\n<p>Perfect for parents who want a reliable, science-backed milk formula, Nan Optipro 3 800g is designed to provide everything your child needs for a healthy, active lifestyle.</p>\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:162:\"Nan Optipro 3 800g: Toddler milk formula with probiotics, vitamins, and minerals to support growth, immunity, and brain development for children aged 1–3 years.\";}s:11:\"\0*\0original\";a:6:{s:2:\"id\";i:95;s:10:\"product_id\";i:95;s:6:\"locale\";s:2:\"en\";s:4:\"name\";s:18:\"Nan Optipro 3 800g\";s:11:\"description\";s:861:\"<p>Nan Optipro 3 800g is a premium toddler milk formula designed for children aged 1&ndash;3 years, offering essential nutrients to support healthy growth, immunity, and brain development. Enriched with probiotics, vitamins, and minerals, this formula helps improve digestive health and nutrient absorption while strengthening the immune system during the crucial toddler years.</p>\n<p>Packed with DHA, calcium, and iron, Nan Optipro 3 promotes the development of strong bones, cognitive function, and overall well-being. As a trusted Nestl&eacute; product, it complements a balanced diet to ensure toddlers receive the nourishment they need for optimal growth and development.</p>\n<p>Perfect for parents who want a reliable, science-backed milk formula, Nan Optipro 3 800g is designed to provide everything your child needs for a healthy, active lifestyle.</p>\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:162:\"Nan Optipro 3 800g: Toddler milk formula with probiotics, vitamins, and minerals to support growth, immunity, and brain development for children aged 1–3 years.\";}s:10:\"\0*\0changes\";a:0:{}s:8:\"\0*\0casts\";a:0:{}s:17:\"\0*\0classCastCache\";a:0:{}s:21:\