(30, 32, 'en', 'Aptamil Infant Formula - Trusted Nutrition for Your Baby\'s Growth', 'Discover Aptamil, a trusted infant formula brand designed to support your baby’s growth and development. Enriched with essential nutrients, prebiotics, and vitamins, Aptamil provides a strong foundation for your little one’s health and well-being. Choose Aptamil for quality and care!'),
(31, 33, 'en', 'Aptamil Stage 1 – 800g | Infant Milk Formula for Newborns', 'Buy Aptamil 1 800g from Probashi Bazar – premium infant formula for 0–6 months. Supports growth, immunity, and brain development.'),
