(72, 142, 'en', 'Similac Gold 1 (800g) – Infant Formula Bangladesh', 'Similac Gold 1 (800 g) – imported infant milk for newborns 0-6 months. Gentle digestion, DHA + Vitamin E for brain & eye growth.'),
