(92, 92, 'en', 'Nestlé Lactogen 2 Follow-Up Formula (650g)', '<p>Nestl&eacute; Lactogen 2 Follow-Up Formula (650g) is specially designed for infants aged 6-12 months. It provides essential nutrients, including proteins, vitamins, and minerals, to support your baby\'s healthy growth and development. This formula is easy to digest, helping ensure your baby receives the right nutrition for their changing needs</p>', 'Nestlé Lactogen 2 (650g) is a follow-up formula designed for infants 6-12 months, providing essential nutrients to support healthy growth and easy digestion.'),
(93, 93, 'en', 'Nestlé Lactogen Probio 3 650g', '<p>Nestl&eacute; Lactogen Probio 3 650g is a premium toddler milk formula designed to support the nutritional needs of children aged 1&ndash;3 years. Packed with probiotics, essential vitamins, and minerals, this formula helps promote healthy growth, strong immunity, and improved digestion during the crucial early years of development.</p>\n<p>With the goodness of probiotic cultures, Lactogen Probio 3 supports a healthy gut, aiding nutrient absorption and digestive comfort. Enriched with calcium, vitamin D, and iron, it contributes to strong bones, brain development, and energy support, while essential vitamins and minerals strengthen natural defenses.</p>\n<p>Created by Nestl&eacute;&rsquo;s trusted expertise in infant and toddler nutrition, Lactogen Probio 3 is crafted to complement a varied diet, giving parents confidence that their child receives balanced, gentle, and nourishing care every day.</p>', 'Nestlé Lactogen Probio 3 650g: toddler milk formula with probiotics, vitamins, and minerals for healthy growth and digestion.'),
(94, 94, 'en', 'Nestlé Lactogen 1 650g', '<p>Nestl&eacute; Lactogen 1 650g is a high-quality infant formula designed for newborns from birth to 6 months. It&rsquo;s enriched with essential nutrients such as calcium, iron, vitamins, and probiotics to support your baby&rsquo;s growth, brain development, and immune system.</p>\n<p>This formula provides optimal nourishment and digestive support, making it the perfect complement to breast milk. Ideal for babies needing a nutritious start in life, Lactogen 1 promotes healthy growth and development, ensuring that your little one receives the care they need during the first stage of life.</p>\n<p>Trusted by parents and backed by Nestl&eacute;&rsquo;s expertise in infant nutrition, Lactogen 1 is the perfect choice for parents seeking a balanced, reliable feeding solution for their newborns.</p>', 'Nestlé Lactogen 1 650g: infant formula with essential nutrients for newborns to support growth, immunity, and early development.'),
(95, 95, 'en', 'Nan Optipro 3 800g', '<p>Nan Optipro 3 800g is a premium toddler milk formula designed for children aged 1&ndash;3 years, offering essential nutrients to support healthy growth, immunity, and brain development. Enriched with probiotics, vitamins, and minerals, this formula helps improve digestive health and nutrient absorption while strengthening the immune system during the crucial toddler years.</p>\n<p>Packed with DHA, calcium, and iron, Nan Optipro 3 promotes the development of strong bones, cognitive function, and overall well-being. As a trusted Nestl&eacute; product, it complements a balanced diet to ensure toddlers receive the nourishment they need for optimal growth and development.</p>\n<p>Perfect for parents who want a reliable, science-backed milk formula, Nan Optipro 3 800g is designed to provide everything your child needs for a healthy, active lifestyle.</p>', 'Nan Optipro 3 800g: Toddler milk formula with probiotics, vitamins, and minerals to support growth, immunity, and brain development for children aged 1–3 years.'),
(96, 96, 'en', 'Nan Optipro 2 800g', '<p>Nan Optipro 2 800g is a scientifically advanced infant formula designed for babies aged 6&ndash;12 months, offering complete nutrition to support healthy growth, immunity, and brain development. Enriched with DHA, probiotics, and essential nutrients, this formula helps strengthen the immune system, support optimal cognitive development, and promote digestive health.</p>\n<p>The DHA (Omega-3 fatty acids) in Nan Optipro 2 plays a key role in brain development, while calcium and iron support the development of strong bones and healthy blood. With probiotics to aid in digestion and improve nutrient absorption, Nan Optipro 2 offers a balanced, easy-to-digest solution for your baby\'s nutritional needs.</p>\n<p>As a trusted Nestl&eacute; product, Nan Optipro 2 provides parents with confidence, ensuring that babies receive the highest quality nutrition for a strong, healthy start in life. Perfect for complementing breast milk and supporting babies through the critical first year of growth and development.</p>', 'Nan Optipro 2 800g: Advanced infant formula with probiotics, DHA, and essential nutrients to support healthy growth, immunity, and brain development for babies aged 6–12 months'),
(97, 97, 'en', 'Nan Optipro 1 800g', '<p>Nan Optipro 1 800g is a premium infant formula designed for babies from birth to 6 months. Enriched with essential nutrients, DHA, and probiotics, it supports your baby&rsquo;s healthy growth, immune system, and brain development during the crucial first months of life.</p>\n<p>Formulated with probiotics, Nan Optipro 1 helps improve digestion and enhance nutrient absorption, ensuring your baby receives the full benefits of each feed. DHA (Omega-3 fatty acids) plays a critical role in the development of the brain and eyes, while calcium and iron promote strong bones and healthy blood.</p>\n<p>Trusted by parents and backed by Nestl&eacute;\'s expertise in infant nutrition, Nan Optipro 1 800g is the perfect complement to breastfeeding, providing a balanced, gentle, and nutritious feeding solution for your newborn.</p>', 'Nan Optipro 1 800g: Infant formula for babies from birth to 6 months, enriched with DHA, probiotics, and essential nutrients to support growth, immunity, and brain development.'),
(98, 98, 'en', 'Nan Optipro 4 800g |', '<p>Nan Optipro 4 (800g) is a premium formula designed to support your toddler&rsquo;s growth and development. Packed with essential nutrients, this milk powder is enriched with high-quality proteins, vitamins, and minerals to help boost immunity, enhance brain development, and promote healthy growth. Ideal for toddlers 2 years and older, Nan Optipro 4 is specially crafted to meet their nutritional needs during this critical stage of development.</p>\n<p>Key Features:</p>\n<p>High-Quality Proteins: Supports optimal growth and development with easy-to-digest proteins.</p>\n<p>Immunity Support: Fortified with vitamins and minerals to strengthen your toddler\'s immune system.</p>\n<p>Brain Development: Contains DHA and ARA, key nutrients that support brain and eye development.</p>\n<p>Balanced Nutrition: Provides essential nutrients for overall health and well-being.</p>\n<p>Suitable for Toddlers 2 Years and Above: Designed for children who are transitioning from infant formula to solid foods.</p>', 'Nan Optipro 4 800g: Toddler milk formula for children aged 3+ years, enriched with DHA, probiotics, and essential nutrients to support growth, immunity, and brain development'),
(99, 99, 'en', 'Similac Gold 1 (800 g) – Newborn Nutrition Formula Bangladesh', '<p>Key Benefits</p>\n<p>Suitable for infants aged 0&ndash;6 months</p>\n<p>Contains DHA, Lutein &amp; Vitamin E for brain and eye development</p>\n<p>Palm-oil-free for easy digestion and soft stools</p>\n<p>Rich in essential vitamins, minerals, and protein for steady growth</p>\n<p>Imported &amp; clinically tested for quality and safety</p>\n<p>Trusted brand by NRB parents and loved by families in Bangladesh</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Product Details</p>\n<p>Brand: Similac (Abbott)</p>\n<p>Origin: Imported (UAE / UK / Singapore variants)</p>\n<p>Weight: 800 g</p>\n<p>Age Group: 0&ndash;6 months</p>\n<p>Storage: Keep in a cool, dry place. Use within 3 weeks after opening.</p>', 'Premium imported baby formula, suitable from birth to 6 months. Balanced nutrients for healthy growth and strong immunity.'),
(100, 100, 'en', 'Similac Gold Stage 2 – Premium Imported Baby Formula 800 g', '<p>Key Benefits</p>\n<p>Suitable for babies aged 6&ndash;12 months</p>\n<p>Enriched with DHA, Lutein &amp; Vitamin E for brain and eye development</p>\n<p>Palm-oil-free for better digestion and nutrient absorption</p>\n<p>Provides complete, balanced nutrition for healthy growth</p>\n<p>Strengthens immunity and supports bone development</p>\n<p>Imported &amp; clinically tested formula trusted by NRB parents</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Product Details</p>\n<p>Brand: Similac (Abbott)</p>\n<p>Origin: Imported (UAE / UK / Singapore variants)</p>\n<p>Net Weight: 800 g</p>\n<p>Age Group: 6&ndash;12 months</p>\n<p>Storage: Keep tightly closed in a cool, dry place. Use within 3 weeks after opening.</p>', 'Similac Gold 2 (800 g) – premium baby milk for growing infants 6–12 months. Palm-oil-free, gentle digestion, and balanced nutritio'),
(101, 101, 'en', 'Similac Gold 3 (800 g) – Toddler Formula for 1–3 Years | Probashi Bazar', '<p>Similac Gold 3 is a premium growing-up formula specially made for toddlers aged 1&ndash;3 years. It provides complete and balanced nutrition to support rapid physical growth, brain development, and strong immunity during the early learning years.</p>\n<p>Formulated with DHA, Lutein, and Vitamin E, Similac Gold 3 helps improve brain and eye development, supporting better learning, focus, and memory. The formula is palm-oil-free, ensuring gentle digestion and improved calcium absorption for stronger bones and teeth.</p>\n<p>Imported and trusted by parents worldwide, Similac Gold 3 (800 g) is now available in Bangladesh through Probashi Bazar, ensuring 100% genuine quality and safe doorstep delivery for your little one&rsquo;s daily nutrition.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Key Benefits</p>\n<p>Suitable for toddlers aged 1&ndash;3 years</p>\n<p>Enriched with DHA, Lutein &amp; Vitamin E for brain and eye development</p>\n<p>Palm-oil-free for better digestion and nutrient absorption</p>\n<p>Supports stronger bones, teeth, and immunity</p>\n<p>Clinically tested and trusted by parents worldwide</p>\n<p>100% authentic imported product from Abbott</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Product Details</p>\n<p>Brand: Similac (Abbott)</p>\n<p>Origin: Imported (UAE / UK / Singapore variants)</p>\n<p>Net Weight: 800 g</p>\n<p>Age Group: 1&ndash;3 years</p>\n<p>Storage: Keep tightly closed in a cool, dry place. Use within 3 weeks after opening.</p>', 'Imported toddler formula for 1–3 years. DHA, Lutein & Vitamin E enriched to support brain, eye, and body development. Palm-oil-free and easy to digest.');
